description: Redevelopment behind retained (part) façade to provide main building comprising basement, ground and six upper floors and corner building of basement, ground and four upper floors with pedestrianised street between main and corner building. Buildings to provide five retail units (Class A1/A3) and community safety office at ground and mezzanine floor, 122 residential units including 37 affordable units on upper floors and 125 car parking spaces, bike park and refuse storage at basement level.
